---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Foundation Marketing Automation"
  description="Foundation marketing automation in Canada. Attract donors, increase grant applications, and grow your foundation impact online."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-900 via-purple-900 to-indigo-900 text-white py-20 md:py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><circle cx=%2250%22 cy=%2250%22 r=%221%22 fill=%22white%22/></svg>'); background-size: 50px 50px;"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <a href="/industries" class="inline-flex items-center text-indigo-300 hover:text-indigo-200 mb-6 transition">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
          </svg>
          All Industries
        </a>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          Marketing Automation for
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400 to-purple-400">Foundations</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-indigo-200 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Grow your donor base, steward major gifts, and amplify impact through intelligent automation.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/book-call" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:from-indigo-600 hover:to-purple-600 transition shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/30">
            Book Your Free Discovery Call
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-indigo-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-indigo-800 transition"><svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>ROI Calculator</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats Section -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white border-b">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-indigo-600 mb-2">71%</div>
          <div class="text-slate-600">Donor retention</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-indigo-600 mb-2">2.8x</div>
          <div class="text-slate-600">Major gift pipeline</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-indigo-600 mb-2">54%</div>
          <div class="text-slate-600">Grant compliance</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-indigo-600 mb-2">$85K</div>
          <div class="text-slate-600">Annual giving growth</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          The Foundation Challenge
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600">
          Major donors require cultivation. Grant compliance demands tracking. Staff is stretched thin. Without systems, opportunities slip away.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Major Gift Cultivation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">High-value donors require personalized touchpoints that staff can't scale manually.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Grant Compliance</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Tracking reporting deadlines and milestones across multiple grants is overwhelming.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Board Engagement</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Board members need regular communication to stay engaged in fundraising.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Impact Reporting</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Donors want to see their investment's impact but reports take forever to compile.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Annual Campaigns</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Year-end giving campaigns need sophisticated multi-touch strategies.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18 9v3m0 0v3m0-3h3m-3 0h-3m-2-5a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM3 20a6 6 0 0112 0v1H3v-1z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">New Donor Acquisition</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Growing the donor base requires systematic outreach beyond existing networks.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          How We Help Foundations
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600">
          Systematize major gift cultivation, automate compliance tracking, and scale impact reporting.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-purple-50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-indigo-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
