            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Major Gift Pipeline</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Automated cultivation sequences move prospects through stages with personalized touchpoints.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Stage tracking</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Personalized touches</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Meeting scheduling</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-purple-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Grant Management</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Never miss a deadline with automated reminders and milestone tracking.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Deadline alerts</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Milestone tracking</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Report templates</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-50 to-red-50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-pink-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Impact Communication</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Automated impact updates keep donors connected to outcomes.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Quarterly reports</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Story updates</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Annual summaries</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-red-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Campaign Automation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Multi-touch annual campaigns with segmentation and personalization.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Donor segmentation</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Year-end campaigns</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Giving Day support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonial -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-purple-50 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-indigo-400 mb-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
