          </blockquote>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl mr-4">
              JL
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Jennifer Liu</div>
              <div class="text-slate-600">Atlantic Canada Education Foundation â€¢ Halifax, NS</div>
